{"tid":1459560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係其中一個係機場留超過六點既人","createTime":"2019-08-12T18:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T05:22:48.000Z","uid":125079,"like":92,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"12d1068b569a054eb605982f4da4712c247005cd","tid":1459560,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:01:49.000Z","msg":"今日一落車已經逼爆咗人, 連門口都入唔到, 最後逼逼埋埋先行到入離境大堂<br />\n<br />\n全部都係着黑衫, 過咗個幾鐘, 機場正式宣佈全日剩低既離境航班全部取消<br />\n<br />\n之後幾個鐘, 一直有好多好多傳言流言, 由防暴警出現, 禁區有黑警, 所有機場員工離開, 機場熄燈, 仲有六點清場<br />\n<br />\n越近六點越多人走, 差唔多走咗六七成人, 但仲有好多手足堅持留低<br />\n<br />\n其實好多留低既本身都係和理非, 我自己都係, 係咁多流言蜚語底下, 仍然堅持留係度, 我相信佢地唔係唔驚, 只係我相信做和理非行動既大家已經開始有一顆勇武既心<br />\n<br />\n因為香港社會已經去到一個離譜到極點既地步<br />\n<br />\n琴晚既事太離譜太暴力, 女仔被爆眼, 近距離行刑性射人, 打到示威者滿臉鮮血, 地鐵站室內放催淚彈, 種種事情令到今日所有有良知既人再次企出黎 <br />\n<br />\n琴晚種種只可以形容為戰爭中先發生既慘況, 令到<span style=\"color: red;\">我地每一個都好絕望好憤怒</span><br />\n<br />\n但今日仍然有咁多人企出黎, 證明暴力係壓迫唔到香港人, <span style=\"color: red;\">班狗警利用記者直播想將暴行比全香港人睇嚇怕我地</span>, 冇人再夠膽上街示威, 記者監督既功用變成佢地宣揚自己暴力行為既工具<br />\n<br />\n但班黑警唔知香港人食軟唔唔食硬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">你越暴力, 我地越嬲<br />\n<br />\n你拉一個, 我地就企十個出黎</span><br />\n<br />\n今日係星期一, 我知今日好多人係請假入黎, 又或者放低咗要做既野, <span style=\"color: red;\">香港機場係成個塞爆咗, 係連行都行唔到 !!! </span><br />\n<br />\n我地要話比全世界聽香港人比恐怖分子黑警襲擊, 琴晚個單係離譜到連啲中立/淺藍都忍唔住口鬧 ( 你地要知道經過721 仲中立扮睇唔到既人係幾難搖動 ) <br />\n<br />\n已經陸陸續續有700幾個手足比狗拉咗, 佢地有人永久失明, 有人手腳斷曬, 有人內傷不止, 佢地犧牲咗自己既前途未來, 而我地有幾千幾萬人都食過催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n我地冇得輸, 我地冇得退, 前線為我地犧牲咗太多, <span style=\"color: orange;\">佢地用自己既身體同鮮血證明比我地睇香港警察係幾咁離譜過分</span>, 亦係佢地每一個既付出犧牲話比我地知, 做一個真真正正既人係要有良知有良心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃藍是政見 黑白是良知 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n為咗一句說話 數十萬人用盡自己既方法去支持, 去延續依場運動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n機場的確係一個好地方, 亦都係對我地每一個人黎講比較安全既地點<br />\n<br />\n唔可以話完全冇危險, 因為班狗真係失曬人性, 琴日既行為基本上同殺人冇分別, 冇人確保到班黑警會唔會獸性大發去搞有咁多外國旅客既機場 <br />\n<br />\n而機場地理位置交通都唔算好, 所以好明白今日咁多人早走既原因, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">但每一個今日仲企出黎仲支持既都係真香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但唔好忘記, 正正係因為人多, 我地先有今日塞爆機場既成果<br />\n<br />\n求下你地一定要堅持落去,我知道要每日塞爆可能好難, 因為大家都有難處, 但每一次如果有召集, 我都一定會義不容辭咁企出黎<br />\n<br />\n我最驚既唔係香港黑警黎清場, 黎捉我<br />\n<br />\n我係驚咁多位香港人唔再留係機場, 唔再山長水遠入黎機場, 我係驚香港人善忘, 三分鐘熱度<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">令機場癱瘓係需要好多好多人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">求下你地,機場係好重要, 求下你地每一次都一齊出黎, 塞爆機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黑警還眼<br />\n<br />\n Don't trust Hong Kong Police</span></span>"},{"pid":"2c301e5803d907fe88cadb601fc8798761093faa","tid":1459560,"uid":125079,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:06:06.000Z","msg":"仲有今日機場一行, 有好多地方要改善<br />\n<br />\n首先: 太多鬼<br />\n<br />\n連登有 tg gp有 現場都有 , 要分清現場同網絡上既虛言, 要搵人更加核實真假, 因為除咗大部分人走咗, 有唔少人以為6點清場最後冇入黎機場<br />\n<br />\n另外 : 要好多好多英文指示同 slogan 海報<br />\n<br />\n越簡單越好 明白因為琴晚發生咁大單野, 今日咁趕仲召集到咁多人出黎, 已經係奇蹟<br />\n<br />\n但英文真係好重要 好多外國旅行睇唔明"},{"pid":"843d0e40141dacd7661ec744c230a2466e175fc0","tid":1459560,"uid":125079,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:09:19.000Z","msg":"真係好驚香港人 唔再出黎 好似200萬人出完 去到最後朗遍地開花只得番幾千幾萬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求下你地每一次都要出黎, 今日既成果大家都見到<br />\n<br />\n我知道每一個出黎香港人都犧牲緊自己某啲野, 或多或少, 但唔好放棄, 唔好善忘, 唔好三分鐘熱度</span></span>"},{"pid":"e2bccbbe15960dc65812a677d10b963bba3ca46f","tid":1459560,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:09:44.000Z","msg":"求求大家，盡快去換美元現鈔！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5e2af9c8295a5b1bd309385e2e34ada581e359ae","tid":1459560,"uid":55463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:11:59.000Z","msg":"因為每個人都驚緊警察私刑同不公平既審判"},{"pid":"914763644439e8b685247cb3daf3dbb0a6ef0cb3","tid":1459560,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:12:43.000Z","msg":"黑警 還眼<br />\n<br />\n黑警 還眼<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"c2af9d3986c863fd1ce7fd56da7f4f2cf471effd","tid":1459560,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:15:38.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我7點先去 6-7點呢段時間幾乎無人入閘<br />\n雖然驚送頭 但我知機場越少人 入面既手足會越危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b930c9e516ed78c22c82cfe2186d6e8577369a5","tid":1459560,"uid":265179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:17:00.000Z","msg":"走左既, 未去既, 聽日同我再入過去塞爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa76988564ae959a3bbe055f008a0a6ddba6eee4","tid":1459560,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:17:04.000Z","msg":"求下你地 一定要每一次都出黎<br />\n<br />\n先可以保護到係裡面既人 <br />\n<br />\n人多 先可以塞爆機場 癱瘓機場"},{"pid":"a2365ea56ab2743eec484f5d5daf46634e634d74","tid":1459560,"uid":4280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:18:00.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"3a4c597dd94522c6ca1e23cda2ee05df17dce5d4","tid":1459560,"uid":71919,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:18:07.000Z","msg":"黃藍是政見 黑白是良知<br />\n呢句正<br />\n<br />\n早啲休息 聽日見"},{"pid":"1169f25313eb7f9d78510f4cf99c07d73a7d06d7","tid":1459560,"uid":145510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不知哪裡來的勇氣夠膽係個咁不利既環境<br />\n諗住同班癲狗玩困獸鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我淨係知無可能dum低留守既手足"},{"pid":"95739a1970026cde2569a967cd4169da87db318f","tid":1459560,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:19:44.000Z","msg":"如果要每一日出 我相信對每個香港人黎講都唔容易<br />\n<br />\n但當每一次有大型召集, 求下你地好似今日咁, 唔好唔記得黑警對香港人做咗啲咩<br />\n<br />\n記住依種感覺 記住依加既一切經歷<br />\n<br />\n每一次都盡量出黎 黎機場<br />\n<br />\n黑警 還眼 <br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"a1af8092826dfcca4adbb6747fdaf2065bc2c4cf","tid":1459560,"uid":125079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1169f25313eb7f9d78510f4cf99c07d73a7d06d7","tid":1459560,"uid":145510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不知哪裡來的勇氣夠膽係個咁不利既環境<br />\n諗住同班癲狗玩困獸鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我淨係知無可能dum低留守既手足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:22:29.000Z","msg":"我都係 越近六點 謠言越黎越多 走既人越黎越多, 個心其實係會有啲驚同緊張, 畢竟環境難撤退<br />\n<br />\n但我睇到現場仲有咁多人留 <br />\n<br />\n仲有旅客同航空公司人員出入<br />\n<br />\n我覺得我需要留係度"},{"pid":"7322e694d0000040f6c2e5ba0dca8e95beba8f44","tid":1459560,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:25:08.000Z","msg":"琴日有幾多絕望有幾嬲既人<br />\n<br />\n今日就會出番咁多人出黎<br />\n<br />\n香港黑警 與民為敵<br />\n<br />\n黑警 還眼 還牙 還番香港比我地"},{"pid":"7e808e136baa81d6dc1099b4d403332bcb0283ab","tid":1459560,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:28:04.000Z","msg":"琴晚訓唔着 今晚都訓唔着<br />\n<br />\n願各位香港人繼續堅持落去"},{"pid":"c6a753361badd2ffd90d24f335f351517c4a524c","tid":1459560,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:28:36.000Z","msg":"揸多粒春袋！<br />\n催淚彈已經係常餐，會唔會有手足去禮賓府開餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a87d33415ff1e819b46644909dc6563e955893b3","tid":1459560,"uid":246118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:28:58.000Z","msg":"有無人有&lsquo;&rsquo;琴日畀人拉咗嘅人&lsquo;&rsquo;嘅消息啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n24個鐘啦，見到律師未？佢地會唔會48個鐘之後都唔放人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34df60a22e340e209423cccfd87c6b7daa20df6c","tid":1459560,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:29:55.000Z","msg":"sorry小妹借位跪求推<br />\n突發！ 點解冇人講816攬炒啦你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456799</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"23517dedfe7fe56e0c6bb8c06779b60f948599b6","tid":1459560,"uid":201837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:30:03.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n簡單同大家分析吓點分fake news<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459508\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459508</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d0a8cb2f7429bd30352e59720eab07b40bdb93da","tid":1459560,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:30:56.000Z","msg":"respect"},{"pid":"9680709abd3fde395e9b06c430eacc20c5727915","tid":1459560,"uid":236140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcaf689e3502c98b1c9e1fdebc565141f35c42b9","tid":1459560,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12d1068b569a054eb605982f4da4712c247005cd","tid":1459560,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:01:49.000Z","msg":"今日一落車已經逼爆咗人, 連門口都入唔到, 最後逼逼埋埋先行到入離境大堂<br />\n<br />\n全部都係着黑衫, 過咗個幾鐘, 機場正式宣佈全日剩低既離境航班全部取消<br />\n<br />\n之後幾個鐘, 一直有好多好多傳言流言, 由防暴警出現, 禁區有黑警, 所有機場員工離開, 機場熄燈, 仲有六點清場<br />\n<br />\n越近六點越多人走, 差唔多走咗六七成人, 但仲有好多手足堅持留低<br />\n<br />\n其實好多留低既本身都係和理非, 我自己都係, 係咁多流言蜚語底下, 仍然堅持留係度, 我相信佢地唔係唔驚, 只係我相信做和理非行動既大家已經開始有一顆勇武既心<br />\n<br />\n因為香港社會已經去到一個離譜到極點既地步<br />\n<br />\n琴晚既事太離譜太暴力, 女仔被爆眼, 近距離行刑性射人, 打到示威者滿臉鮮血, 地鐵站室內放催淚彈, 種種事情令到今日所有有良知既人再次企出黎 <br />\n<br />\n琴晚種種只可以形容為戰爭中先發生既慘況, 令到<span style=\"color: red;\">我地每一個都好絕望好憤怒</span><br />\n<br />\n但今日仍然有咁多人企出黎, 證明暴力係壓迫唔到香港人, <span style=\"color: red;\">班狗警利用記者直播想將暴行比全香港人睇嚇怕我地</span>, 冇人再夠膽上街示威, 記者監督既功用變成佢地宣揚自己暴力行為既工具<br />\n<br />\n但班黑警唔知香港人食軟唔唔食硬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">你越暴力, 我地越嬲<br />\n<br />\n你拉一個, 我地就企十個出黎</span><br />\n<br />\n今日係星期一, 我知今日好多人係請假入黎, 又或者放低咗要做既野, <span style=\"color: red;\">香港機場係成個塞爆咗, 係連行都行唔到 !!! </span><br />\n<br />\n我地要話比全世界聽香港人比恐怖分子黑警襲擊, 琴晚個單係離譜到連啲中立/淺藍都忍唔住口鬧 ( 你地要知道經過721 仲中立扮睇唔到既人係幾難搖動 ) <br />\n<br />\n已經陸陸續續有700幾個手足比狗拉咗, 佢地有人永久失明, 有人手腳斷曬, 有人內傷不止, 佢地犧牲咗自己既前途未來, 而我地有幾千幾萬人都食過催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n我地冇得輸, 我地冇得退, 前線為我地犧牲咗太多, <span style=\"color: orange;\">佢地用自己既身體同鮮血證明比我地睇香港警察係幾咁離譜過分</span>, 亦係佢地每一個既付出犧牲話比我地知, 做一個真真正正既人係要有良知有良心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃藍是政見 黑白是良知 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n為咗一句說話 數十萬人用盡自己既方法去支持, 去延續依場運動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n機場的確係一個好地方, 亦都係對我地每一個人黎講比較安全既地點<br />\n<br />\n唔可以話完全冇危險, 因為班狗真係失曬人性, 琴日既行為基本上同殺人冇分別, 冇人確保到班黑警會唔會獸性大發去搞有咁多外國旅客既機場 <br />\n<br />\n而機場地理位置交通都唔算好, 所以好明白今日咁多人早走既原因, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">但每一個今日仲企出黎仲支持既都係真香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但唔好忘記, 正正係因為人多, 我地先有今日塞爆機場既成果<br />\n<br />\n求下你地一定要堅持落去,我知道要每日塞爆可能好難, 因為大家都有難處, 但每一次如果有召集, 我都一定會義不容辭咁企出黎<br />\n<br />\n我最驚既唔係香港黑警黎清場, 黎捉我<br />\n<br />\n我係驚咁多位香港人唔再留係機場, 唔再山長水遠入黎機場, 我係驚香港人善忘, 三分鐘熱度<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">令機場癱瘓係需要好多好多人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">求下你地,機場係好重要, 求下你地每一次都一齊出黎, 塞爆機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黑警還眼<br />\n<br />\n Don't trust Hong Kong Police</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:35:17.000Z","msg":"我都唔驚 只係目標已達成 走得 日日塞其實遲啲打擊經濟方面一樣有好大成果 同埋旅客keep走唔到過多幾日自然唔會有arrival可以來 最緊要係大家可以返屋企抖 24小時真係唔係人人都會響應<br />\n不過見到巴絲打係機場照顧旅客都支持 但萬事一定要小心<br />\n<br />\n利申 今日已經帶哂底褲嗰啲去"},{"pid":"8441b478128836bd132fb242b16f5b8531a8e961","tid":1459560,"uid":236140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6387d8e320aae0a1964353645625e9fa9f43a9","tid":1459560,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:42:03.000Z","msg":"大家一齊入機場睇飛機升降<br />\n<br />\n參觀下香港國際機場依個咁偉大既建築物"},{"pid":"901a02e587ae743af14a17b13a1c30b7e9f18d1a","tid":1459560,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:45:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"40ff6ccb4d3c639a7e6cb504b04dbaae71e1a1d2","tid":1459560,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:45:32.000Z","msg":"其實今日已經好好 由琴晚恐怖襲擊發生到召集去機場 <br />\n<br />\n一日都冇 已經塞爆咗機場<br />\n<br />\n證明香港人今次真好嬲"},{"pid":"648b2d5235d1c1b6dca16c9e59d8c42080134488","tid":1459560,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:48:41.000Z","msg":"各位 撐住 機場見"},{"pid":"c40e5e1ed09713178ff14bd530b3de7eb16fb776","tid":1459560,"uid":263443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:56:10.000Z","msg":"入去一齊討論機場作戰戰術呀！！！！<br />\n<br />\n《和你飛 無限之戰》戰術討論整理<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459625\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459625</a>"},{"pid":"f2cab9f1ba75529802d77687766e803b61c00588","tid":1459560,"uid":263443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:58:33.000Z","msg":"入去一齊討論機場作戰戰術呀！！！！<br />\n<br />\n《和你飛 無限之戰》戰術討論整理<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459625\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459625</a>"},{"pid":"dd34d4f3080bd7d379cf1790d57a451b235a9716","tid":1459560,"uid":264174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:59:11.000Z","msg":"聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebbb67ad7fb428b5b4cb164d517e8ff1894c226e","tid":1459560,"uid":265696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"